(70, 1, '2015-04-07 09:53:44', '2015-04-07 14:53:44', '<h2>A Few Words About Us</h2>\r\nPHP/IOP are alternative levels of care, designed to assist clients with re-integration into the community after an in-client stay or to prevent in-client hospitalization for mental health issues. Clients benefit from individualized, innovative care that eliminates the institutionalized feel of traditional hospitals. Clients are encouraged to collaborate in their care, and all efforts are made to provide the most cutting-edge treatment available.\r\n\r\nOur unique atmosphere allows clients to continue medication management, individual, family, and group therapy prior and post admission to the PHP/IOP programs, allowing clients to access services that fit their individual needs. Clients can build a lasting relationship with their clinicians, thus reducing multiple admissions and promoting continuity of care.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://dev.mindabovematter.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/BlueRibbonAward.png"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-307 alignleft" src="http://dev.mindabovematter.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/BlueRibbonAward-300x178.png" alt="BlueRibbonAward" width="300" height="178" /></a>\r\n\r\n[zilla_button url="/schedule" style="link" size="large" type="round" target="_self"] Schedule Your Appointment [/zilla_button] [zilla_button url="/what-to-expect" style="grey" size="large" type="round" target="_self"] What To Expect [/zilla_button]', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-05-07 16:24:39', '2015-05-07 21:24:39', '', 0, 'http://dev.mindabovematter.com/?page_id=70', 0, 'page', '', 0),
