(265, 1, '2015-04-22 14:45:15', '2015-04-22 19:45:15', '<h2>Mind Above Matter Career Opportunities</h2>\nMind Above Matter is a small company that provides a quality work environment for all current and potential employees. We recognize the importance of having employees who enjoy where they work and whose main goal is to passionately and innovatively care for the people we serve. If interested in inquiring about our current positions, please contact Dr. Reshaunda Strickland at<a href="mailto:reshaunda.strickland@innovativepsych.org">reshaunda.strickland@innovativepsych.org</a>\n\n[zilla_button url="mailto:jackie.todd@innovativepsych.org" style="link" size="large" type="round" target="_self"] Email us about employment [/zilla_button]\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe always welcome interns. We typically have positions available for counseling interns, social work interns, receptionist interns, and medical billing interns. If interested in inquiring about our current availability, please contact Jackie Todd at<a href="mailto:jackie.todd@innovativepsych.org">jackie.todd@innovativepsych.org</a>\n\n[zilla_button url="mailto:jackie.todd@innovativepsych.org" style="link" size="large" type="round" target="_self"] Email us about internship [/zilla_button]', 'Career Opportunities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '75-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-22 14:45:15', '2015-04-22 19:45:15', '', 75, 'http://dev.mindabovematter.com/75-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
